message: “Human trafficking is profiting from humans, anything from sex to labor,” Ennis said. “It’s all throughout Florida as well. There could be 50 people living in the back part of a restaurant you never see. There could be employees of a restaurant picked up with a van and housed at night. That could be human trafficking as well, the community needs to keep its eyes open.”
